### CSS: two distinct animated backgrounds

```css
.wd-modal-overlay { position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 1100; background: rgba(6,10,8,.6);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 16px;
  animation: wdFadeIn .18s ease-out both; }
@keyframes wdFadeIn { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }

/* Confirm card: soft breathing glow behind the sheet */
.wd-confirm-card { position: relative; border-radius: 18px; overflow: hidden;
  animation: wdPopIn .24s cubic-bezier(.2,1,.3,1) both; }
@keyframes wdPopIn { from { transform: translateY(10px) scale(.98); opacity: 0; } to { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); opacity: 1; } }
.wd-confirm-bg { position: absolute; inset: -40%; z-index: 0; pointer-events: none; overflow: hidden; }
.wd-confirm-blob { position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; filter: blur(38px); animation: wdBreathe 4.5s ease-in-out infinite; }
.wd-confirm-blob-a { width: 220px; height: 220px; top: -40px; left: -50px; background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent) 0%, transparent 70%); opacity: .35; }
.wd-confirm-blob-b { width: 200px; height: 200px; bottom: -60px; right: -40px; background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent-warm) 0%, transparent 70%); opacity: .22; animation-delay: 1.4s; }
@keyframes wdBreathe { 0%,100% { transform: scale(.92); opacity: .2; } 50% { transform: scale(1.12); opacity: .4; } }

/* Pending card: spinning ring + pulsing dots under the clock icon */
.wd-pending-ring { position: absolute; top: 14px; width: 84px; height: 84px; border-radius: 50%;
  border: 3px solid transparent; border-top-color: var(--accent-warm); border-right-color: rgba(245,158,11,.25);
  animation: wdSpin 1.6s linear infinite; }
.wd-pending-dot { position: absolute; top: 52px; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent-warm);
  animation: wdDotPulse 1.8s ease-in-out infinite; }
.wd-pending-dot-1 { left: calc(50% - 26px); animation-delay: 0s; }
.wd-pending-dot-2 { left: calc(50% - 3px);  animation-delay: .3s; }
.wd-pending-dot-3 { left: calc(50% + 20px); animation-delay: .6s; }
@keyframes wdSpin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
@keyframes wdDotPulse { 0%,100% { opacity: .25; transform: scale(.8); } 50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.15); } }
```

### Notification handlers for withdraw approve/reject (no centered modal — toast + inbox is enough here, unlike deposits)

```js
onLive('withdraw:approved', ({ transaction }) => {
  toast(`Withdrawal approved! GHS ${transaction.amount} sent.`, 'success');
  addNotification({ id: `withdraw-approved-${transaction.id}`, title: 'Withdrawal approved', body: `GHS ${transaction.amount} has been sent to your mobile money.`, kind: 'withdraw_approved' });
});
onLive('withdraw:rejected', ({ transaction, reason }) => {
  toast(`Withdrawal of GHS ${transaction.amount} rejected${reason ? ': ' + reason : ''}. Refunded.`, 'warn');
  addNotification({ id: `withdraw-rejected-${transaction.id}`, title: 'Withdrawal rejected', body: `Your GHS ${transaction.amount} withdrawal was rejected${reason ? ': ' + reason : '.'} The amount has been refunded to your balance.`, kind: 'withdraw_rejected' });
});
// wallet:update already handles the actual balance refund display —
// this handler is purely for the "why did my balance change" explanation.
```

